message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. This item is truly exceptional and has been meticulously crafted to meet your needs. Given its value and quality, I believe it would be a perfect fit for you. Considering its worth, I am offering it to you for $11,500. This price reflects the product's high value and ensures you receive a great deal. I trust this offer will allow us to reach an agreement that benefits both of us.
